This a Object Oriented approach to the card game of war. It use use enums to create the ranks and suits of cards in a deck. The enums are put into a card class. 
This card class contains all the information needed about a card. The Card class is put into a deck class that deals with all of the cards. The deck also creates
the entire deck of cards. 

To build:
1. "mkdir build"
2. "cmake .."
3. "make"
4. "./war"

The actual gameplay of war is contained in the Deck class. The deck class function play() starts the game after the Deck class initalizes the deck. 